# ===== Documentation & Reference Files =====
# Keep important project documentation, ignore generated reference docs
# Important project files (keep)
!README.md
!**/README.md
!DEPLOYMENT.md
!PHASE_1_COMPLETE.md
!plan-*.prompt.md

# Generated/temporary reference docs (ignore)
NOTES.md
notes.md
TODO.md
todo.md
PROJECT_STATUS.md
project-status.md

# Design files (ignore - these are temporary references)
design.md
DESIGN_TEMP.md
spec.md
SPEC_TEMP.md
architecture_notes.md
ARCHITECTURE_NOTES.md
